FBIS4-62668 "drsov096_g_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-096 Daily Report 16 May 1994 WESTERN REGION Belarus Russian Ruble May Be in Circulation in 1-2 Months Russian Ruble May Be in Circulation in 1-2 Months LD1605183394 Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy in Russian 1500 GMT 16 May 94 LD1605183394 Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy Russian BFN [Text] Belarus Prime Minister Vyacheslav Kebich has said during a working visit to Borisov, that the Russian ruble could be in circulation in Belarus within one to two months. He reiterated that the union of monetary systems is necessary for taking the economy of Belarus out of its present crisis.
